    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ぉ……朝よぉ……起きなさぁい……\n朝ご飯は、お味噌汁の佃煮が作った琴乃よぉ……",
      "startTime": 104,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9400.000000000005,
          "startTime": 113.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "んん……怜……？　寝ぼけてるの……？\nふわぁ……あれ……うぅ、まだ全然早い時間じゃない",
      "startTime": 119.1,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 18800.00000000001,
          "startTime": 137.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "もっと寝かせて……怜も寝てていいからぁ……\nんしょ……そうだ、お誕生日おめでとぉ……すぅ……",
      "startTime": 137.9,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 22666.666666699995,
          "startTime": 160.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ……？　寝てていいのぉ……？\nあれ、マカロンだ。美味しそぉ……あむ……うま",
      "startTime": 153.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "んん、ふわぁ……。なんかさっき、怜が来たような……\n気の所為かしら……って、あれ、体が動かない……",
      "startTime": 178.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "んん～……お腹一杯……",
      "startTime": 185.2666784288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "え……ちょ、えぇ！？　なんで怜が一緒に寝てるの！？\nひゃっ、変なとこ触らないでよ……！",
      "startTime": 194.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "もぉ……どうなってるのよ。あれ、マカロンが\n食べ散らかされてる……これ、明らかに……",
      "startTime": 206.4000071208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、プレゼントする予定だったし、別にいいけど……\n寝ぼけた怜は、酔っ払った遙子さんなみに厄介ね",
      "startTime": 219.3560908958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "怜、起きて。ねぇ、早くしないと遅刻するわよ\nさっきは起きれたでしょ？",
      "startTime": 230.3000071208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoktnroom-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoktnroom-00-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_53_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "んううう……\n寝てていいって言ったの、琴乃でしょぉ……",
      "startTime": 235.1000071208,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.326212500004,
          "startTime": 242.3333333333
